{"tid":1488321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民間真普選] 政府唔落實真普選 市民自行實行真普選","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T14:45:26.000Z","uid":4672,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c4dcf243e523f88a37c3323fadb9daeded95488a","tid":1488321,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:57:24.000Z","msg":"用籌集既資金 我地市民自己開真普選選舉<br />\n全港18區 一人一票投臨時政府官員<br />\n先真普選投臨時議會 全部18區議席按比例代表制直選<br />\n然後臨時議會提名特首候選人 再交由市民一人一票投出<br />\n<br />\n最後再係國際上尋求承認  美國澳洲英國一眾民主政府一定會承認我地民主選舉出黎既政府<br />\n變相架空港共 架空北京  我地市民自己實行真普選 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0733cb7fc79361bb7baf5609516b93b46358ec1f","tid":1488321,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:04.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ecb9403efa1fb030bd0a36f447e35a26020f0924","tid":1488321,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"眾籌預埋我"},{"pid":"f5a7ac766698ab0cb50a55a77a70901f928d2723","tid":1488321,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:58:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">阻阻大家 入黎擺低死線唔該<br />\n既然無死線做唔到野就擺低死線既日期出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家個個話要死線 死線呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"898a6363e4f8056fe662af774a62dcdd00bf3c2a","tid":1488321,"uid":4672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c4dcf243e523f88a37c3323fadb9daeded95488a","tid":1488321,"uid":4672,"like":0,"disli